ble overhead. Finally we demonstrate, how dynamic\nperformance tuning can be integrated into a real-world application from\ncryo-electron microscopy domain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 16:46:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2020 11:26:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-02"}
