w solid-state\nplatform based on moir\\'e superlattices which can be used to simulate\noutstanding problems in strong correlation physics that are manifested by\ntriangular lattice Hubbard models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Oct 2019 01:20:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-22"}
