strengths\nsuggests optimistic prospects of increasing $\\theta_c$ and achieving correlated\nstates with large $U/W$ effective interaction versus bandwidth ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Oct 2019 14:52:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
